019-07-18T00:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n標題明明戒糖 究竟我睇緊乜野"},{"pid":"45f302055feba586c211cc2a8830f25ecdac8bfd","tid":1325382,"uid":279963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:30:37.000Z","msg":"食到咁因住行出街暈低<br />\n絲打? 幾高? 幾重?<br />\n我建議你朝早o個個太陽餅變成4~5隻蛋白好過<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/egg-whites-nutrition#nutrition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fnutrition%2Fegg-whites-nutrition%23nutrition&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSWg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=dc464d7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/egg-whites-nutrition#nutrition</a><br />\n一隻蛋白都係得4g protein, 16calories<br />\n就算你改到食5隻都係20g protein, 80calories<br />\n再睇一睇太陽餅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.myfitnesspal.com/zh-TW/food/calories/taiwan-food-sun-cake-63355185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.myfitnesspal.com%2Fzh-TW%2Ffood%2Fcalories%2Ftaiwan-food-sun-cake-63355185&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSWg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=3ba6fb6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.myfitnesspal.com/zh-TW/food/calories/taiwan-food-sun-cake-63355185</a><br />\n我當你一啖係1/3個, 都已經有77 calories, 但只有1g protein<br />\n更加唔好提佢係糖多, 脂肪多, 仲要用豬油.<br />\n話說將塊麵包改成食全麥麵包<br />\n然後再食d nuts好過"},{"pid":"788c94354b3e38987828937d13a77efebdd7535b","tid":1325382,"uid":279963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:31:18.000Z","msg":"順便宣傳下:<br />\n[碌鳩成長日記] 分享健身經歷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328164\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328164</a>"},{"pid":"6a2cbd0ce90a5f9484d70cfb0164c88ad260be35","tid":1325382,"uid":184094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ea49b0c5815ee5cd99f796f19ebc1079447b405","tid":1325382,"uid":87828,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:50:58.000Z","msg":"麵包兩塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma